<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-32-0824 </DOCNO><TEXT>Part I of this study was presented at 41st ABM Congress in 1986, and PartII was presented at the II Encontro do Hemisferio Sul sobre TecnologiaMineral, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil in 1987. In this paper (Part III) methodsfor calculating and adjusting mass balances are discussed with specialreference to their application to gravimetric beneficiation of coals.Software in Basic was developed to this end utilizing operating datafrom jigging plants. It is concluded that these techniques are very usefulfor the quantification of errors in sampling and the physical and chemicalanalysis of samples.</TEXT></DOC>